    <div class="wpd-comment-left ">
    <div class="wpd-avatar ">
    <img alt="Barbara Roberts" src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2f8d6d8718520ee8a15a7aabbf220e37?s=64&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=g" srcset="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2f8d6d8718520ee8a15a7aabbf220e37?s=128&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=g 2x" class="avatar avatar-64 photo" height="64" width="64" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
